    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i had this small cyst removed by my doctor a few days ago here in sydney and the cut looks a bit weird today. it's kinda red and feels warm if i touch it, and there's some yellowish stuff oozing out a little bit. is that normal or should i be worried? i really dont want to go back to the clinic if i dont have to",
