      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the reassurance. i was worried it might be an infection but that makes me feel better. do you think i can just treat it at home to speed things up? like if i just put some antibiotic ointment from the chemist on it and use a warm compress every few hours to keep it clean, that should be fine right? i'd rather just handle it myself than deal with the doctor again.",
